description:
Available at: https://openstudionetwork.com/keezer - Designed with more advanced players in mind, these videos contain a powerful arsenal of tools to give you total control and a true sense of freedom when playing "outside" the chord changes. Includes: 

• 5 Chord Turnarounds - via an analysis of John Coltrane's solo on "Resolution"
• Two Things at Once - 3 videos of challenging exercises to stretch your brain
• We've Got You Surrounded -  surrounding chords chromatically (includes a demonstration of a new composition)  
• Anything Goes - putting it all together and giving you wings!
• PDF's 

Great for any instrument!  

Level: Advanced
